Agent EVAL Report — 2026-06-10
================================

Branch: research/embedding-branch vs main (baseline)
Seed vault: vidbrain_vault (612 notes, expanded to 632)
Test videos: 38 (3 skipped — file not found)
Valid pairs: 36

Results:
  dim A (terminology):  -0.14  (tie)
  dim B (wikilinks):    -0.94  (main wins)
  dim C (suggestions):  +0.00  (tie)
  dim D (overall):      emb 0% win rate

Self-doubt: dimension B flagged in 81% of reviews

Conclusion: NO_MERGE

Root cause:
  1. RAG context format pollutes LLM judgment — wikilink syntax
     ([[note_name]]) in RAG context text causes LLM to create
     spurious wikilinks to unrelated notes
  2. Technical term over-correction on non-technical content
  3. All 36 pairs were "existing domain" (seed vault had related
     notes), so this eval primarily measures RAG interference
     rather than RAG benefit

Recommendations for next iteration:
  - Remove [[wikilink]] syntax from RAG context strings
  - Use plain note names: "相关笔记: NoteName" instead of "[[NoteName]]"
  - Consider a separate eval with truly "new domain" videos
